-- Provider: Cloudnine Hospital (formerly The Birthplace)
INSERT INTO provider.provider (id, name, provider_type_id, about, phone, is_verified, is_registered_user)
VALUES (734645, 'Cloudnine Hospital (formerly The Birthplace)', 1, 'The Birthplace (now Cloudnine) is a premium birthing facility located in Hyderabad, Telangana. The Birthplace was established with the intent to create a memorable experience of childbirth for a mother and her family. With 25 well-equipped rooms, designed keeping needs and comfort of the mother and the baby, the Birthplace offers a host of pre and postnatal services including Neonatal Intensive Care Unit, Childbirth Education sessions, Yoga and Lamaze classes, Mother & Baby exercises, Diet and Nutrition advice, and counseling. The Birthplace strongly believes that childbirth is a unique event in one’s life that requires clinical attention as well as focus on the mother’s overall wellness and therefore follows an integrated approach that makes the delivery of a child a memorable, joyful and hassle-free occasion.

The Birthplace is also proud to have been rated the No.1 hospital for gynecology & obstetrics in Hyderabad, for the third year running. Incidentally, we are also being ranked No.1 in South India and No.2 in the country.

4 Great Reasons to Deliver at the Birthplace
===================================
 
1)  No conditions apply on our delivery packages!
 
     The price of your delivery, which is the same for a normal or a C-section delivery, is communicated to you at the time you book your delivery which is the exact same amount that will be billed to you when you check out. In other words, no hidden costs or nasty last-minute surprises!
 
2)  Wait for your baby. Not for your appointment. 
 
      There is no reason why you should be made to wait endlessly to meet your doctor or to get your scan or tests done. We value your time just as you do. Not only will your appointment be on time, but our doctors also spend ample time with you to answer each and every one of your questions - big or small.
 
3)  What about visiting hours? You tell us.
 
      Every hour is a visiting hour at the Birthplace. That said, we''re aware that some moms like to be surrounded by family and friends almost every minute of the day, while others tend to take their privacy a little more seriously. So, it''s entirely up to you. 
You decide when you would like visitors, and we''ll be happy to follow your orders.
       
4)  The best plan ever made. The Birth Plan.

      You love plans. We love plans. And together, we can plan every detail of your baby''s birth which should help you be less Stressed and a lot more in control. The objective of the birth plan, very simply, is to help you feel confident and liberated, Instead of anxious and unsure. It also includes personalized, interactive counselling sessions with the family.
 
 
Before You Make the Big Decision, Take A Little Tour
----------------------------------------------------------------------------

We''d like you to experience the Birthplace at your own pace. Please feel free to bring your husband, or a friend or relative, and take the personalized tour, where it will be our pleasure to show you around.
Expect to be introduced to every nook and cranny - right from the cafeteria on the ground floor to the LDR suites on the fourth, and from the Living Room (a ''living'' space that functions as a library, theatre, chat room, yoga Centre and more) to the well-stocked baby boutique and the NICU.

All ending in a nice cup of hot chocolate (or a cold coffee, should you so prefer).', '+914041891800', true, false)
