INSERT INTO provider.provider (id, name, provider_type_id, about, phone, is_verified, is_registered_user)
VALUES (734966, 'Oliva Skin & Hair Clinic', 1, 'Oliva started its journey back in 2009 with its first 3 flagship clinics in Hyderabad. What started as a vision to offer personalized treatment solutions for one and all, Oliva has now expanded its professional services across several states within India. Oliva stands tall with 23 state-of-the-art and conveniently located clinics that offer exclusive services and high-end procedures supervised by an experienced team of dermatologists. With its 6 clinics in Hyderabad, 7 in Bangalore, 3 each in Chennai and Kolkata, 2 in Pune and 1 each in Vizag and Kochi; Oliva boasts of highest quality standards and specializes in imparting pioneering medical and cosmetic dermatological expertise with a sole objective to transform and truly enhance the lives of the clients.
Our highly efficacious and customized dermato-trichology services set up apart from others and strive us toward growth to constantly emerge as the market leaders while keeping the clients’ needs at the core.
Our Vision
We, at Oliva, are constantly guided by our vision – “to be the leading skin and hair clinic in India, seek to deliver customized and technology-based competent services, excel in client satisfaction, emerge as market leaders in revenues, client and employee satisfaction.”
Our Values
Our values stand tall as our pillars of strength and usher our vision in totality. Oliva has a ‘Client First’ policy, as clients are in the heart of whatever we do. We strive for the highest client satisfaction rate. Next comes colleagues. Oliva works as a team with communication, experience, corroboration and dedication each time to build loyalty, innovate and exceed client expectations while adding value to the company. The experts at Oliva yearn to combine their in-depth research and hands-on experience with strong ethical values to build a strong culture into evolving wellness needs, reminiscing of the key doctrines of our institution – transparency, dignity, integrity and passion to excel.
Why are we the Right Choice?
• A wide spectrum of treatment solutions and services concerning skin and hair
• State-of-the-art, ambient clinics with advanced USFDA approved equipment
90 + highly experienced team of dermatologists with excellent knowledge, hands-on experience and credentials
• Comprehensive one-on-one consultation with the doctors
• Extensive and rigorous training at regular intervals with a thoroughly updated understanding of upcoming technologies
• Client-first approach with highly customized services
• Strong value system designed to deliver the highest level of client satisfaction
• Highest quality standards and protocols designed to deliver the best results





Our USP – The Core Values That Have Shaped Us Into Who We Are

With 23 clinics pinned across the length and breadth of India, our emphasis is entirely on offering world-class services powered by the latest innovations and technologies in the field of dermatology. We strongly adhere to our values which have helped us come a long way to help us grow and emerge as one of the leaders in skin and hair services. With a team of 90 + doctors and 400+ clinic operations employees, Oliva is leading continually towards success under their supervision, knowledge and expertise. Oliva has been able to successfully carve a niche to guide individual clients into their journey to great skin and hair health forming a large client base.
By bringing the synergy of novel concepts of aesthetic dermato-trichology with equipment having USFDA’s stamped approval and expertise of trained aestheticians, Oliva has a single-minded focus on imparting tailored solutions to a wide array of skin and hair ailments. Oliva stands apart and ahead in delivering flawless skin and hair solutions through the use of the latest technologies. Oliva’s efforts to leverage client’s unique needs with the utmost support, care, safety and holistic approach have helped transform their lives and boost confidence.
Our success story
Oliva takes pride to have been ranked number 1 clinic in dermatology and trichology by Times of India for four consecutive years in a row. This is a testimony to our hard work, consistent efforts and diligent focus on delivering nothing but the best to our clients. The experts at Oliva are recognized to have pioneered medical expertise along with cutting-edge innovations in the field of aesthetic dermatology through rigorous training and unparalleled dedication.
Our customized treatment modalities and solutions are backed by science to give real results. The technology used in imparting these services conforms to USFDA standards to provide safe and scientific solutions along with paramount client satisfaction.
Since its inception, Oliva follows a holistic approach to offer in-depth insight into the client’s skin and hair ailments and develop advanced aesthetic treatment solutions customized to one’s needs. We have been on our toes to make every step of our client journey rewarding and empowering.
Specialized Treatments and Services Offered At Oliva
• Hair growth treatment – Oliva offers expert hair regrowth treatment solutions to treat almost any stage of hair loss. From hair rejuvenation using oral and topical medications to natural and non-invasive platelet-rich plasma (PRP) for hair regrowth and restoration, our holistic treatments use USFDA approved equipment to give lasting results for healthier hair and scalp.
• Acne and scar treatment – Our customized treatments to treat acne and remove or lighten acne scars include chemical peels, laser treatment using Pixel fractioned erbium YAG technology and Q Switched Nd YAG laser and Microneedling using radiofrequency technology among others. We assure you that you will leave our clinic with radiant, bright and flawless skin.
• Laser hair removal – Oliva brings the most sophisticated technology offering a permanent solution to reduction in unwanted hair on any part of the body. Our USFDA approved Suprano ice, Nd YAG and SHR technology ensure painless, fast and cost-effective treatment.
• Anti-aging treatment – Oliva’s signature anti-aging treatments include botox, fillers and laser treatments to re-sculpt your face giving a refreshed appeal. These treatments will reduce and alter the effects of aging to bring back a rejuvenated and youthful complexion.
• Skin rejuvenation treatment – Our skin rejuvenation treatments such as laser toning, chemical peels, microdermabrasion, and body polishing are customized to your ski’s unique needs to work on even the most dehydrated skin and make it radiant, plump and supple.
• Body treatments – Our newly launched treatments aimed at getting a slim, toned and contoured physique have gained popularity for their fast results. These non-surgical treatments include Inch Loss treatment, body sculpting treatment, weight loss and weight management treatment.
• Other treatments – Oliva offers safe, virtually painless and minimally invasive procedures for unwanted tattoo removal, mole, warts and stretch mark removal anywhere from the body.', '+914049170030', true, false)
