VALUES (697654, 'Oliva Skin & Hair Clinic', 1, 'Oliva started its journey back in 2009 with its first 3 flagship clinics in Hyderabad. What started as a vision to offer personalized treatment solutions for one and all, Oliva has now expanded its professional services across several states within India. Oliva stands tall with 23 state-of-the-art and conveniently located clinics that offer exclusive services and high-end procedures supervised by an experienced team of dermatologists. With its 6 clinics in Hyderabad, 7 in Bangalore, 3 each in Chennai and Kolkata, 2 in Pune and 1 each in Vizag and Kochi; Oliva boasts of highest quality standards and specializes in imparting pioneering medical and cosmetic dermatological expertise with a sole objective to transform and truly enhance the lives of the clients.
