QUA Nutrition is one of the pioneer Nutrition companies with branches in India as well as E- clinics spread all across. The genesis of this organization is the realization that there are lacunae when it comes to health and sports based nutrition in India. The science of nutrition counselling and implementation in daily life as a lifestyle input and change is still at the experimental stage in the world.
QUA Nutrition as a company has made Nutritional Counselling a specialization that is customized to each person’s own diet and needs. We employee some of the most talented and the best Nutritionist in the country, who handle clientele of all walks of life throughout India and across the world. We have diet plans/advice for everyone, including infants, toddlers, children, adolescents, adults and sports persons.
