-- Provider: FMS Dental Hospital
INSERT INTO provider.provider (id, name, provider_type_id, about, phone, is_verified, is_registered_user)
VALUES (1133053, 'FMS Dental Hospital', 1, 'FMS Dental Hospitals established in 1993, with over a million patients treated, has been widely recognized as one of the worlds’ leading and most preferred Dental Care Service Provider in Asia, especially the Middle East Region. It is in fact now rated as the Best dental center in the country and 5th in the world, according to Global Clinic Rating (GCR). With the introduction of new International Dental Center at Jubilee Hills, FMS Dental is at the brink of setting another bench mark of Dental care delivery in India. The new facility is mainly focused on international patients and dental tourism, maintaining global standards in dental care.
The facility is state-of-the-art, spread over a vast space with ample parking, elevator, cosy lounges on every floor for patient privacy and comfort, in-house cafeteria and spacious treatment rooms. It is truly dentistry revisited, wherein patients undergo dental treatment in an absolutely stress free, relaxed environment. The clinics are equipped with world class dental operatories from Castellini, Chirana and SkanRay for optimum comfort. Sterilization and Infection control begins right from the doorstep maintaining OSHA standards, using the most advanced B-class & Doc Autoclaves and liberal use of disposables, ensuring a zero bacteria environment.

Having all the specialties of dentistry under one roof, this center is unique having the first TMD clinic established in the state of Telangana equipped with BIOPAK system to diagnose temperomandibular joint pain and related problems. The Biopak diagnostic system includes the JVA (jaw vibration analysis), Tekscan, Jaw tracker, Electomyogram and TENS therapy too, offering a sigh of relief for those people suffering from undiagnosed facial pains for long time. The LASER Dentistry clinic is powered with a plethora of Hard and Soft tissue LASERs like the FOTONA Er-YG / Nd-YG and Diode LASERs from CAVO, SIROLASE, SUNNY, LITEMEDICS etc, for the most safe and conservative LANAP gum procedures, Root canal disinfections, minor oral surgeries etc.
This International center houses an exclusive Dental Implant clinic with the top notch Implantologists available round the week. Offering all the top international brands of Implants this facility  is also one of the few in India to have an inhouse CBCT, CAD/CAM supported Dental Lab, digital impression making and shade matching. What makes this center complete is the availability of conscious sedation and general anesthesia facility for the pediatric and dental phobia patients, with a senior anesthetist and maxillofacial surgeons on call round the clock.FMS rechristened as Face Makeover and Smile clinics lives true to its name here, by uniting the stalwarts from all disciplines of dentistry creating a comprehensive Cosmetic Dentistry team like none other. Here, these Smile Engineers recreate those lost smiles with Digital smile designing, lumineers, laminates, professional tooth whitening, composite bonding, metal free crowns etc, working hand-in-hand with the dental technicians in the center’s own state-of-the-art dental lab. In the last 2 decades, Brand FMS has been fast gaining a reputation of being one of the finest Implantology and Cosmetic dentistry centers’ in the country, catering to a lot of international and high profile patients. Individual personalized care with highly skilled senior doctors trained nationally/internationally add to this beautiful hospital with a spa like atmosphere, taking dentistry to another level and give you a dental experience like none other. With this new center, FMS sure has given people from all over the world, another reason to visit Hyderabad!!!', '+914041891805', true, false)
