-- Provider: Zoi Health
INSERT INTO provider.provider (id, name, provider_type_id, about, phone, is_verified, is_registered_user)
VALUES (1367652, 'Zoi Health', 1, 'ZOI Hospitals was established in 2015 at Somajiguda, Hyderabad and is a 104 bedded super specialty Orthopaedic hospital with the most modern facilities and equipment. It is a fully air-conditioned hospital with 4 Operation Theatres and a host of specialties and services.

ZOI was started with a singular mission to give world-class and exceptional quality service in the musculoskeletal disorders, disease, and dysfunction, to everyone. In this short span, ZOI has already carved a niche in the area of Orthopedics, Emergency & Trauma, Internal Medicine and Critical care.

ZOI – A way of life The vision behind the beginning of ZOI was to have an institute where extraordinary orthopaedic treatment is pioneered with the intention to make patients get back to active living at the earliest. While their bodies being fit is the focus, we at ZOI believe they should leave the hospital ready and confident to take on life.

At ZOI, all actions are driven by commitment- a place where doctors are proud to belong. The vision is to create institutes for not only innovation in technique and equipment but also pioneering the way orthopaedic care is delivered. In these times of distrust of the medical field, ZOI endeavours to bring transparency and accountability to delivering health care.

Today at ZOI, everyone and everything is driven by passion – passion to excel, passion to provide exceptional care, passion to deliver the good, passion to get trained and developed- all with utmost empathy. You will feel the difference the moment you step in.

The Team ZOI vision has appealed to a lot of eminent doctors, who are extremely successful and pioneers in their own field, to tie up and be a part of the vision. Today the core ortho team is the backbone of the hospital and works together to give each patient the maximum advantage. It is made up of 9 Orthopaedicians with experts in all disciplines of this field (we think it is the most cohesive orthopaedic team in the twin states), ably supported by Internal medicine specialists (Internists), Intensivist, Anaesthetist and Pain Management specialists, Plastic Surgeons, Vascular Surgeons, Neurosurgeons, Wound care specialists.

There is a very committed and skilled physiotherapy team and Dietician too. Together, ZOI brings to you a team of meticulous experts who will ensure that your health is in the safest of hands.

Considering the time constraint for working professionals, ZOI caters to the needs of patients across the city in the late evenings every day & even on Sunday. We have doctors available till 8pm at somajiguda and 9 pm at attapur, where we encourage our patients to come in leisurely post their work hours. ZOI acknowledges the needs of the patients & provides necessary care.Our singular mission to give world-class and exceptional quality service at worthwhile cost, stays true to this day with the most cohesive team of doctors taking forth care to new heights. With Zoi, care is key and so are the possibilities you can garner from an active lifestyle after your meet us. The main philosophy of Zoi is to understand and empathize with your pain and provide therapy which is suitable to what you need.

Zoi is one of the top 10 critical care services at Hyderabad as per TOI survey in 2016. We strive to extend our reach to as many patients as possible with multiple locations and 24/7 emergency trauma services. In this era, we dedicatedly provide holistic care with empathy to break the stigma of hospitals being commercialized. The perception of people is changing and most of our patients come to us through word of mouth because of their experience here.Our goal is to handle every treatment with excellence, integrity, empathy, effectiveness, and responsiveness.', '+914041891798', true, false)
